\input pdftexcmds.sty\relax
\def\msg#1{%
  \begingroup
    \escapechar=92 %
    \immediate\write16{#1}%
  \endgroup
}
\long\def\test#1#2#3#4{%
  \begingroup
    #4%
    \def\str{%
      Test \string\pdf@isprimitive
      {\string #1}{\string #2}{...}: %
    }%
    \pdf@isprimitive{#1}{#2}{%
      \ifx#3Y%
        \msg{\str true ==> OK.}%
      \else
        \errmessage{\str false ==> FAILED}%
      \fi
    }{%
      \ifx#3Y%
        \errmessage{\str true ==> FAILED}%
      \else
        \msg{\str false ==> OK.}%
      \fi
    }%
  \endgroup
}
